## Log scores of win predictions

~~~{.R}
logScore <- function (obs, pred) {Reduce("+", na.omit(unlist(Map(function (o,p) {
                                                                  if (o) {log(p)} else {log(1-p)} },
                                                                 obs, pred))))}
~~~

Example of the difference between Brier and log score:

~~~{.R}
